OL,5, Families with disabled children who    
OL,6, rely on specialist medical equipment   
OL,7, say they are facing impossible choices 
OL,8, as energy bills in the UK soar.        
OL,10,FSome 5,500 families took part in a     
OL,11,Fsurvey by leading disability charity   
OL,12,FContact, shared with the BBC, about the
OL,13,Fimpact of increasing energy costs.     
OL,15,FAlmost 2,000 families said they feared 
OL,16,Ftheir child's condition would get worse
OL,17,Fas a result of rising prices.          
OL,19,FThe government said support was        
OL,20,Favailable to help with fuel bills.     
